{"tid":867450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姚松炎：東大嶼人工島項目將虧損5900億元","createTime":"2018-10-18T16:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T15:34:22.000Z","uid":92301,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"54b421484c21785675223d3bdc856d4b7e1973da","tid":867450,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"這兩天有讀者查詢如何計算東大嶼人工島項目的盈利/虧蝕率，特此簡介如下 (更詳細的DCF計法可個別教授)：<br />\n<br />\n1。關於總開發成本9500億元，可參考我在星期日明報的計法 [1]。(以2023年造價計算，未計MOD)<br />\n<br />\n2。根據施政報告以110萬人口為上限，假設每戶平均人數為2.7人，即共需約40萬伙住宅。(若以下限計算，收入更低)<br />\n<br />\n3。以每伙平均750平方英尺建築面積計算，即共3億平方英尺住宅樓面面積<br />\n<br />\n4。公私營7:3比，即私樓樓面面積為9000萬平方英尺<br />\n<br />\n5。以每尺賣地價4000元計(2023年AV價)，共收3600億港元[2]。(假設增加了這麽多土地，2023年地價仍不跌，否則虧蝕更嚴重。這賣地價數字與建制派議員相同)<br />\n<br />\n6。換言之，項目總虧蝕5900億元 (3600億-9500億)，虧蝕率約為60%。<br />\n<br />\n[1] 姚松炎 (2018) 明日大嶼的投資分析，明報 10月14日。<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181014/s00005/1539453980507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181014%2Fs00005%2F1539453980507&d=ziwUO1pVl6ACsftRMy3zUm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ed033241\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181014%2Fs00005%2F1539453980507&h=064c3c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181014/s00005/1539453980507</a><br />\n<br />\n[2] 不計算非住宅地出售及資助房屋出售金額，因為成本未有計及興建資助房屋成本及開發核心商業區的額外成本<br />\n<br />\n[3] 假設地積比率為5 (已屬較高密度，一般新市鎮為3.5)，私樓用地面積為1800萬平方英尺，約佔總面積1700公頃的10.6%，即住宅總用地合共600公頃，約佔全島面積的35%，已超出一般規劃上限的30%，反映貴細擠不變，仍然虧蝕嚴重！<br />\n<br />\n[4] 由於虧蝕率高，發債需要支付利息，將會令虧蝕更嚴重。(以上計算假設零息)<br />\n<br />\n[5] 大家可以據此計算粉嶺高球場和棕地的盈利/虧蝕率，三者比較後再決定那一選項對未來幾代人最合適和最有利。這是我在議會時建議的挪威模式，向市民提供最少三個選項的可行性比較，讓公眾在充足資訊下作出選擇，而不是連價格都未清楚就決定上馬！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sosreader.com/n/@ecyY/5bc708ebfd89780001d694a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsosreader.com%2Fn%2F%40ecyY%2F5bc708ebfd89780001d694a8&d=ziwUO1pVl6ACsftRMy3zUm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d7290ae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sosreader.com/n/@ecyY/5bc708ebfd89780001d694a8</a>"},{"pid":"71b760dd1337b6b58c2d75d1d9aa24a5ead2baaf","tid":867450,"uid":61280,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一吹我已經屌左：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼，今日水魚！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過最大既魔鬼唔係賺蝕，而係依萬幾兩萬億既地極可能又係支共買，到時必又有借口焗港豬哽大lot印爆冥紙變做HKD！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0312a81565de5918a18305d0f3dbc4fb0bbab6f4","tid":867450,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966f5fb68f64aa01717a4e343f522306fbd7cf1a","tid":867450,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ca6249b70c787d76dfe380321a19eb93a3e76f","tid":867450,"uid":54681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da19a0f00efc3a86bc4a11880f2c67f4551566bb","tid":867450,"uid":176553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:45:32.000Z","msg":"仲未計商用地？"},{"pid":"752a6344c4b717a82b592cc36059fde3069c5ee3","tid":867450,"uid":151071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:49:34.000Z","msg":"有地鐵直通西環同埋南面無限海景都係賣4000蚊呎，算唔算良心政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba29d4e1332bb699722057098e2a6bdcc8648218","tid":867450,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:58:40.000Z","msg":"香港地每2.7人住750尺嘅話 無人屌政府啦😂"},{"pid":"449cb5f5d001c2c94a3637b4b0c82931b2417f7b","tid":867450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">5。以每尺賣地價4000元計(2023年AV價)，共收3600億港元[2]。(假設增加了這麽多土地，2023年地價仍不跌，否則虧蝕更嚴重。這賣地價數字與建制派議員相同)<br />\n</span><br />\n雖然話供應大增同埋樓價有升有跌，但係分階段落成影響應該唔大<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[2] 不計算非住宅地出售及資助房屋出售金額，因為成本未有計及興建資助房屋成本及開發核心商業區的額外成本<br />\n</span><br />\n興建資助房屋個成本同收入根本係另一盤數，由房協揹或者額外注資。你要計收支ge話，根本唔洗起公屋居屋啦<br />\n開發核心商業區有咩額外成本？鋪utilities？"},{"pid":"f04bf5d9587be793e6ac60c728891b97cee55c29","tid":867450,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有地鐵直通西環同埋南面無限海景都係賣4000蚊呎，算唔算良心政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2beeb0f9ed6182c250f5d43fdf291a70935a6e","tid":867450,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a6ea3148dee9b06b68e42036100ce12e3c978414","tid":867450,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da19a0f00efc3a86bc4a11880f2c67f4551566bb","tid":867450,"uid":176553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:45:32.000Z","msg":"仲未計商用地？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma