rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依D市民得益又唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1820eece9c8c0278bdc6ad2badeb0e07969bc5d5","tid":867450,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6ea3148dee9b06b68e42036100ce12e3c978414","tid":867450,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da19a0f00efc3a86bc4a11880f2c67f4551566bb","tid":867450,"uid":176553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:45:32.000Z","msg":"仲未計商用地？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每塊住宅地皮中，已包括商業樓面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"根據施政報告以110萬人口為上限，假設每戶平均人數為2.7人，即共需約40萬伙<span style=\"color: red;\">住宅</span>。(若以下限計算，收入更低)<br />\n<br />\n3。以每伙平均750平方英尺建築面積計算，即共3億平方英尺<span style=\"color: red;\">住宅樓面面積</span><br />\n<br />\n4。公私營7:3比，即<span style=\"color: red;\">私樓樓面面積</span>為9000萬平方英尺<br />\n<br />\n人地由頭到尾用住宅面積計算推論，點樣可以得出9000萬平方英尺包括商業樓面?"},{"pid":"9f8f7dc26535efb033dfe0deeff248192775b6cf","tid":867450,"uid":54142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93923743f06ee8d810105f0609e1c259c929c119","tid":867450,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T00:05:57.000Z","msg":"當年鳩鐵諮詢時造價都係140~170億<br />\n結果呢?<br />\n<br />\n人工又唔見佢升4,5倍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n一萬億只係保守估計<br />\n回歸後大型工程超支倍係幾何級數上<br />\n到最後變成5萬億10億元其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6a372df49c4a39ef3c093d8288d1002d35885d","tid":867450,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec9d307b50f994655066bb503495d7dc7a5906e","tid":867450,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"係咪益班內房架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97e772b9c86efdc07fa5ae9d00e560e27a3185e","tid":867450,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"香港要地<br />\n<br />\n而家一係比大陸佬買砂做顧問做工程<br />\n<br />\n一係比錢班新界佬屯地波地產商買地<br />\n<br />\n新界佬地產佬就一定反你個填海<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁香港市民如果兩個方法都唔想嘅話，仲會唔會有第三個方案比到出黎？"},{"pid":"099696ff5e4e99f97520780f4ebd5174a233368b","tid":867450,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}